#. ID 1, Page 2, Line 36, Pos (36,24)
#. ID 2, Page 2, Line 36, Pos (36,25)
msgid ""
"...What's going on?\\!\n"
"I hear a humming sound\n"
"in my pocket..."
msgstr ""
"…どうしたんだろう？\\!\n"
"ポケットの中から何かの音が聞こえる…"

#. ID 3, Page 2, Line 3, Pos (17,27)
msgid ""
"Someone here to see me?\\!\n"
"I'm sure you've caught wind\n"
"of my genius and couldn't\n"
"help but see, yes?"
msgstr ""
"何者かが、この私に会いに来たようね？\\!\n"
"ジョージの天才っぷりを風の便りに聞き、\n"
"どうしても会いたくて\n"
"ここまで訪れた来た。そうなのでしょう？"

#. ID 3, Page 2, Line 8, Pos (17,27)
msgid "Um-\\.\\.\\^"
msgstr "えっと…\\.\\.\\^"

#. ID 3, Page 2, Line 10, Pos (17,27)
msgid ""
"Don't answer!\\!\n"
"Of course you are.\\!\n"
"What else could you\n"
"possibly want?"
msgstr ""
"答えは要らない!\\!\n"
"もちろん、そうなのだから。\\!\n"
"だって、他に何を求めてくるっていうの？"

#. ID 3, Page 2, Line 15, Pos (17,27)
msgid ""
"I have a question.\\!\n"
"Can you please answer?"
msgstr ""
"質問があるんだ。\\!\n"
"答えてくれるかな？"

#. ID 3, Page 2, Line 18, Pos (17,27)
msgid ""
"Of course!\\!\n"
"I know everyting.\\!\n"
"And if I don't know,\n"
"my books well tell me."
msgstr ""
"もちろん!\\!\n"
"私は何でも知っているのだから。\\!\n"
"たとえ知らないことがあっても、\n"
"本が教えてくれるわ。"

#. ID 3, Page 2, Line 23, Pos (17,27)
msgid ""
"How could I get into\n"
"the tower?"
msgstr "どうやって塔に入るのかな？"

#. ID 3, Page 2, Line 26, Pos (17,27)
msgid ""
"...\\.My books will\n"
"need to tell me this\n"
"one."
msgstr ""
"…\\.それは私の本が\n"
"教えてくれるでしょう。"

#. ID 3, Page 2, Line 29, Pos (17,27)
msgid ""
"Or at least they would,\n"
"but its so DREADFULLY\n"
"boring."
msgstr ""
"少なくともそうだけれど、\n"
"でもそれってとーっても退屈。"

#. ID 3, Page 2, Line 32, Pos (17,27)
msgid ""
"As you can clearly\n"
"see, I enjoy books.\\!\n"
"Strange books.\\!\n"
"Wonderful books."
msgstr ""
"お分かりのように、私は本を\n"
"楽しんでるの。\\!\n"
"奇妙な本。\\!\n"
"素晴らしい本。"

#. ID 3, Page 2, Line 36, Pos (17,27)
msgid ""
"Can't you bring me\n"
"something interesting?\\!\n"
"Maybe that will motivate\n"
"someone as fabulous as me."
msgstr ""
"何か面白いものをくれないかしら？\\!\n"
"そうすれば、私のような素晴らしい人の\n"
"モチベーションも上がるかもしれないわ。"

#. ID 3, Page 2, Line 49, Pos (17,27)
msgid ""
"Oh? What's this?\\!\n"
"Hm... it looks like it's written\n"
"in an ancient language."
msgstr ""
"あら、これは何かしら？\\!\n"
"えぇと…古代の言語で\n"
"書かれているようだわ。"

#. ID 3, Page 2, Line 52, Pos (17,27)
msgid ""
"Nothing I can't\n"
"understand.\\!\n"
"I'll need some peace\n"
"I translate this."
msgstr ""
"ジョージに理解できないものはない。\\!\n"
"解読するのに、少し集中力が要りそう。"

#. ID 3, Page 2, Line 60, Pos (17,27)
#. ID 3, Page 3, Line 53, Pos (17,27)
#. ID 3, Page 4, Line 39, Pos (17,27)
#. ID 3, Page 5, Line 49, Pos (17,27)
#. ID 3, Page 6, Line 45, Pos (17,27)
#. ID 3, Page 7, Line 45, Pos (17,27)
msgid "I think I'm hungry."
msgstr "お腹が空いたみたい。"

#. ID 3, Page 2, Line 62, Pos (17,27)
#. ID 3, Page 2, Line 78, Pos (17,27)
msgid ""
"There's a cafe to the\n"
"southeast somewhere.\\!\n"
"Now shoo and leave\n"
"my magnificence be."
msgstr ""
"南東のどこかにカフェがあるわ。\\!\n"
"惜しいかもしれないけれど、\n"
"壮麗なジョージから、少し離れる時間よ。"

#. ID 3, Page 2, Line 69, Pos (17,27)
msgid ""
"Chop chop.\\!\n"
"My beautiful young face\n"
"is only getting older."
msgstr ""
"ビシバシ!\\!\n"
"早くしないと、ジョージの美しい顔が\n"
"老けていってしまうわ。"

#. ID 3, Page 2, Line 87, Pos (17,27)
msgid ""
"I did it.\\!\n"
"As expected of someone\n"
"of my ability."
msgstr ""
"できたわ。\\!\n"
"さすがジョージ。"

#. ID 3, Page 2, Line 90, Pos (17,27)
msgid "Take a look."
msgstr "見てごらんなさい。"

#. ID 3, Page 2, Line 95, Pos (17,27)
#. ID 13, Page 1, Line 64, Pos (11,25)
msgid ""
"I have faith that you'll save me.\\!\n"
"I mean, who wouldn't?"
msgstr ""
"あなたは私を救うと信頼しているわ!\\!\n"
"誰だって、そうするでしょう？"

#. ID 3, Page 3, Line 3, Pos (17,27)
msgid ""
"Who the hell are you\n"
"supposed to be?"
msgstr "アンタ一体何者？"

#. ID 3, Page 3, Line 6, Pos (17,27)
msgid "..."
msgstr "…"

#. ID 3, Page 3, Line 8, Pos (17,27)
msgid ""
"Well?\\!\n"
"Out with it."
msgstr ""
"それで？\\!\n"
"何の用かしら。"

#. ID 3, Page 3, Line 11, Pos (17,27)
msgid ""
"My name is Niko.\\!\n"
"I'm trying to reach the\n"
"spire."
msgstr ""
"ミーの名前はニコ。\\!\n"
"塔に行きたいんだ。"

#. ID 3, Page 3, Line 15, Pos (17,27)
msgid ""
"Oh, right.\\!\n"
"You've got that lightbulb."
msgstr ""
"あらそう。\\!\n"
"電球を持ってるものね。"

#. ID 3, Page 3, Line 17, Pos (17,27)
msgid ""
"Listen. You're just some\n"
"tool the world will use\n"
"to heal itself."
msgstr ""
"よく聞きなさい。\n"
"アンタは世界自身を癒すための\n"
"道具に過ぎないの。"

#. ID 3, Page 3, Line 20, Pos (17,27)
msgid ""
"If you want my help,\n"
"you need to help me\n"
"first.\\!\n"
"Understand?"
msgstr ""
"アタシの助けが必要ってんなら、\n"
"まずアタシを助けて欲しいのよ。\\!\n"
"分かる？"

#. ID 3, Page 3, Line 24, Pos (17,27)
msgid ""
"Find me a book I've\n"
"never seen before.\\!\n"
"That's the deal."
msgstr ""
"アタシが見たことない本を見つけるのよ。\\!\n"
"それが条件。"

#. ID 3, Page 3, Line 28, Pos (17,27)
msgid "...Okay."
msgstr "…分かった。"

#. ID 3, Page 3, Line 38, Pos (17,27)
msgid ""
"What's this old thing?\\!\n"
"Huh, it's written in an\n"
"ancient language."
msgstr ""
"この古いのは一体何なの？\\!\n"
"へえ、古代の言語で書かれてるのね。"

#. ID 3, Page 3, Line 41, Pos (17,27)
msgid ""
"Guess you are useful.\\!\n"
"Now go make yourself\n"
"even more useful and leave\n"
"me alone while I translate."
msgstr ""
"アンタも役に立つのね。\\!\n"
"アタシが解読してる間、\n"
"アンタはアタシを放っておいて。\n"
"その方がアタシのためになるのよ。"

#. ID 3, Page 3, Line 45, Pos (17,27)
msgid ""
"I'll help you with the\n"
"tower after I'm done.\\!\n"
"It's not like I want to\n"
"die, after all."
msgstr ""
"終わった後、塔に行くのを助ける。\\!\n"
"別に、死にたいわけじゃないわよ。"

#. ID 3, Page 3, Line 55, Pos (17,27)
#. ID 3, Page 3, Line 68, Pos (17,27)
msgid ""
"Go bother the people\n"
"in the cafe southeast\n"
"of here."
msgstr ""
"ここの南東にあるカフェの人に\n"
"迷惑でもかけてくるのよ。"

#. ID 3, Page 3, Line 61, Pos (17,27)
msgid "Hurry up."
msgstr "さっさとね。"

#. ID 3, Page 3, Line 76, Pos (17,27)
msgid ""
"I'm finished.\\!\n"
"You're definitely going\n"
"to want to take a look\n"
"at this."
msgstr ""
"終わったわ。\\!\n"
"これは絶対に読んでおいた方がいいわよ。"

#. ID 3, Page 3, Line 84, Pos (17,27)
msgid "Don't screw this up, please."
msgstr "お願いだから、しくじるんじゃないわよ。"

#. ID 3, Page 4, Line 3, Pos (17,27)
msgid ""
"Si\\.i\\.i\\.\\.i\\.\\.igh.\\!\n"
"Hi."
msgstr ""
"は\\.あ\\.あ\\.あ\\.あ\\.\\.ぁ…\\!\n"
"こんばんは。"

#. ID 3, Page 4, Line 6, Pos (17,27)
msgid ""
"...\\.Hi.\\!\n"
"I'm looking for a way\n"
"into the spire."
msgstr ""
"…\\.こんばんは。\\!\n"
"ミー、塔に入る方法を探してるんだ。"

#. ID 3, Page 4, Line 10, Pos (17,27)
msgid ""
"Oh. Dunno.\\!\n"
"It'll probably be\n"
"in one of my books."
msgstr ""
"あぁ。知らない。\\!\n"
"私の本のどれか1冊に\n"
"書かれてるかもしれないけど…"

#. ID 3, Page 4, Line 13, Pos (17,27)
msgid ""
"I really don't feel\n"
"like looking, though.\\!\n"
"I'm so bored."
msgstr ""
"探すのが好きじゃなくて…\\!\n"
"すごく退屈だから。"

#. ID 3, Page 4, Line 16, Pos (17,27)
#. ID 3, Page 4, Line 47, Pos (17,27)
msgid ""
"Please find me some new\n"
"book that could entertain\n"
"me.\\!\n"
"Si\\.i\\.i\\.\\.i\\.\\.igh."
msgstr ""
"お願いだから、何か私が楽しめるような、\n"
"新しい本を見つけてほしいの。\\!\n"
"は\\.あ\\.あ\\.あ\\.あ\\.\\.ぁ…"

#. ID 3, Page 4, Line 29, Pos (17,27)
msgid ""
"Oh.\\!\n"
"It's written in an\n"
"ancient language."
msgstr ""
"ああ。\\!\n"
"古代の言語で言語で書かれてるみたいね。"

#. ID 3, Page 4, Line 32, Pos (17,27)
msgid ""
"How... interesting.\\!\n"
"I must translate this.\\!\n"
"I'll help you when I'm done."
msgstr ""
"なんて…興味深いの。\\!\n"
"これは、私が解読しないと。\\!\n"
"終わったら、あなたを手伝うわ。"

#. ID 3, Page 4, Line 41, Pos (17,27)
#. ID 3, Page 4, Line 57, Pos (17,27)
msgid ""
"There's a cafe.\\!\n"
"Southeast.\\!\n"
"Go."
msgstr ""
"カフェがある…\\!\n"
"南東。\\!\n"
"行ってきて。"

#. ID 3, Page 4, Line 65, Pos (17,27)
msgid ""
"Done.\\!\n"
"Check it out."
msgstr ""
"できた。\\!\n"
"見てみて…"

#. ID 3, Page 4, Line 71, Pos (17,27)
#. ID 13, Page 1, Line 106, Pos (11,25)
msgid ""
"Death sounds so boring.\\!\n"
"Don't let it happen."
msgstr ""
"死ぬのって、とっても退屈そう。\\!\n"
"それは…やめてほしいわ。"

#. ID 3, Page 5, Line 3, Pos (17,27)
msgid ""
"Hello~!\\!\n"
"Who might you be?"
msgstr ""
"やっほー!\\!\n"
"キミ、誰かな？"

#. ID 3, Page 5, Line 6, Pos (17,27)
msgid ""
"Hello! My name is\n"
"Niko.\\!\n"
"I'm looking for a way\n"
"into the spire."
msgstr ""
"こんばんは!ミーの名前はニコだよ。\\!\n"
"塔に入る方法を探してるんだ。"

#. ID 3, Page 5, Line 11, Pos (17,27)
msgid ""
"Hello Niko!\\!\n"
"I'm sorry, but I don't\n"
"know a way inside..."
msgstr ""
"こんばんは、ニコ!\\!\n"
"ごめんね、中に入る方法は\n"
"分かんないんだ…"

#. ID 3, Page 5, Line 15, Pos (17,27)
msgid "O-Oh, it's okay."
msgstr "あ、あぁ、大丈夫だよ。"

#. ID 3, Page 5, Line 17, Pos (17,27)
msgid ""
"Hm...\\. Maybe one of\n"
"my books has the key.\\!\n"
"I'll help you find it if\n"
"you help me!"
msgstr ""
"ふーむ…\\.わたしの本が\n"
"カギになってるのかも。\\!\n"
"手伝ってくれるなら、探してあげるよ!"

#. ID 3, Page 5, Line 21, Pos (17,27)
msgid ""
"I want more books!\\!\n"
"Something new and\n"
"interesting!"
msgstr ""
"もっと本が欲しいんだ!\\!\n"
"新しくって、面白いもの!"

#. ID 3, Page 5, Line 24, Pos (17,27)
msgid "Just one will do~!"
msgstr "1冊でいいからー!"

#. ID 3, Page 5, Line 26, Pos (17,27)
msgid "I'll see what I can find!"
msgstr "何か探してみるよ!"

#. ID 3, Page 5, Line 37, Pos (17,27)
msgid ""
"Oh my!\\!\n"
"What's this?"
msgstr ""
"ひゃー!\\!\n"
"何これ?"

#. ID 3, Page 5, Line 39, Pos (17,27)
msgid ""
"...\\.It's written in an\n"
"ancient language!\\!\n"
"Oh my goodness~!"
msgstr ""
"…\\.古代の言語で書かれてる!\\!\n"
"わわー!"

#. ID 3, Page 5, Line 42, Pos (17,27)
msgid ""
"Lemme translate it,\n"
"pleeeease?\\!\n"
"I'll help you when I'm done!"
msgstr ""
"おねがーい、翻訳させて？\\!\n"
"終わったら手伝うからさ!"

#. ID 3, Page 5, Line 51, Pos (17,27)
msgid ""
"There's yummy food\n"
"in the cafe southeast\n"
"of here!\\!\n"
"Why not visit them for a bit?"
msgstr ""
"ここの南東のカフェ、美味しいものが\n"
"いっぱいなんだ!\\!\n"
"行ってみたらどうかな？"

#. ID 3, Page 5, Line 58, Pos (17,27)
msgid "You can do it~!"
msgstr "キミならできるー!"

#. ID 3, Page 5, Line 65, Pos (17,27)
msgid ""
"This is hard...\\!\n"
"Gimme a few minutes,\n"
"'kay?"
msgstr ""
"難しい…\\!\n"
"ちょっと時間をくれないかな？"

#. ID 3, Page 5, Line 73, Pos (17,27)
msgid ""
"Oh, hello! I'm done!\\!\n"
"You should read it...\\!\n"
"It seems really important..."
msgstr ""
"あ、やっほー!できたよ!\\!\n"
"これは読むべきだね…\\!\n"
"とっても重要だと思う…"

#. ID 3, Page 5, Line 80, Pos (17,27)
#. ID 13, Page 1, Line 126, Pos (11,25)
msgid "We're all counting on you!"
msgstr "私たち、みんなキミに期待してるよ!"

#. ID 3, Page 6, Line 3, Pos (17,27)
msgid ""
"Oh hello, sweetie.\n"
"Aren't you adorable?\\!\n"
"I didn't know the light-bearer\n"
"would be so cute."
msgstr ""
"あらこんばんは、かわいこちゃん。\n"
"とっても愛らしいわね!\\!\n"
"光を運ぶ子がこんなに可愛らしいなんて\n"
"思わなかったわ。"

#. ID 3, Page 6, Line 8, Pos (17,27)
msgid ""
"U-\\.Um...\\!\n"
"Thank you..."
msgstr ""
"えっ、\\.と…\\!\n"
"ありがとう…"

#. ID 3, Page 6, Line 11, Pos (17,27)
msgid ""
"Do you know how to\n"
"enter the tower, miss?"
msgstr ""
"お姉さん、どうやって塔に入るか\n"
"知ってる？"

#. ID 3, Page 6, Line 14, Pos (17,27)
msgid ""
"I don't, but I could help\n"
"you find a book that\n"
"could."
msgstr ""
"いいえ、でもそういう本を見つける\n"
"手伝いはできるわ。"

#. ID 3, Page 6, Line 17, Pos (17,27)
msgid ""
"But first, could you be\n"
"a sweetheart and bring\n"
"me a new book for my\n"
"collection?"
msgstr ""
"ただその前に、その優しい心で\n"
"私のコレクションのための新しい本を\n"
"持ってきてくれないかしら？"

#. ID 3, Page 6, Line 21, Pos (17,27)
msgid ""
"It's a policy I'm afraid\n"
"I can't change even for\n"
"you!"
msgstr ""
"残念ながら、たとえあなたのためでも\n"
"変えられないポリシーなの!"

#. ID 3, Page 6, Line 33, Pos (17,27)
msgid ""
"How interesting.\\!\n"
"A journal written in\n"
"an ancient language."
msgstr ""
"何て興味深いの。\\!\n"
"古代の言語で書かれた日記のようね。"

#. ID 3, Page 6, Line 36, Pos (17,27)
msgid ""
"I'm sure you'd like\n"
"this translated, wouldn't\n"
"you, sweetie?"
msgstr ""
"これを解読してほしいのかしら、\n"
"かわいこちゃん？"

#. ID 3, Page 6, Line 39, Pos (17,27)
msgid ""
"Give me some time to\n"
"work, please."
msgstr "少し時間をくれないかしら。"

#. ID 3, Page 6, Line 47, Pos (17,27)
msgid ""
"There's a cafe southeast\n"
"of here."
msgstr "ここの南東にカフェがあるわ。"

#. ID 3, Page 6, Line 49, Pos (17,27)
msgid ""
"I'm sure the people\n"
"there can fix you\n"
"up something nice."
msgstr ""
"あそこの人なら、きっといいものを\n"
"用意してくれるわ。"

#. ID 3, Page 6, Line 55, Pos (17,27)
msgid ""
"Please be quick,\n"
"darling."
msgstr "できるだけ早くね、おちびさん。"

#. ID 3, Page 6, Line 63, Pos (17,27)
msgid ""
"I'm sure the people in\n"
"the cafe can fix you\n"
"up something nice."
msgstr ""
"カフェの人なら、きっといいものを\n"
"用意してくれるわ。"

#. ID 3, Page 6, Line 71, Pos (17,27)
msgid ""
"Welcome back, darling.\\!\n"
"You might want to have a\n"
"look at this..."
msgstr ""
"おかえり、おちびさん。\\!\n"
"これを見てほしいんだけど…"

#. ID 3, Page 6, Line 78, Pos (17,27)
#. ID 13, Page 1, Line 147, Pos (11,25)
msgid ""
"I know you'll make the right\n"
"choice at the top of the spire."
msgstr ""
"貴方が塔の頂上で正しい選択をするのは\n"
"分かっているわ。"

#. ID 3, Page 7, Line 3, Pos (17,27)
msgid ""
"Hey pal, what's up?\\!\n"
"Can I get you anything?"
msgstr ""
"やっほーーどしたの？\\!\n"
"何か困りごと？"

#. ID 3, Page 7, Line 6, Pos (17,27)
msgid ""
"Uh, hi.\\!\n"
"I'm looking for a way\n"
"into the spire."
msgstr ""
"えっと、やあ。\\!\n"
"塔に入る方法を探してるんだ。"

#. ID 3, Page 7, Line 10, Pos (17,27)
msgid ""
"Oh. I dig it, buddy.\\!\n"
"I'm sure one of my books\n"
"will help us out."
msgstr ""
"オー。いいじゃん、チビくん。\\!\n"
"たぶんウチの本が助けになるっしょ。"

#. ID 3, Page 7, Line 13, Pos (17,27)
msgid ""
"Can you get me a\n"
"new book or something\n"
"first though?\\!\n"
"All of mine are totally lame."
msgstr ""
"その前にさー、なんか新しい本くれなーい？\\!\n"
"もーウチの本ぜーんぶダサいカンジでさあ。"

#. ID 3, Page 7, Line 18, Pos (17,27)
msgid "Oh, sure. I guess."
msgstr "えっと、うん。探してみるよ。"

#. ID 3, Page 7, Line 20, Pos (17,27)
msgid ""
"Gnarly!\\!\n"
"Thanks a ton!"
msgstr ""
"ワーオ!\\!\n"
"マジサンキュー!"

#. ID 3, Page 7, Line 31, Pos (17,27)
msgid "Woah, what IS this?"
msgstr "ワーオ、何コレ？"

#. ID 3, Page 7, Line 32, Pos (17,27)
msgid ""
"It's written in an\n"
"ancient language!\\!\n"
"That's so sick!"
msgstr ""
"古代の言語で書かれてるし!\\!\n"
"マジスゲー!"

#. ID 3, Page 7, Line 35, Pos (17,27)
msgid ""
"I bet I could translate\n"
"this in... a couple of minutes!\\!\n"
"I can translate this before\n"
"I help you, right?"
msgstr ""
"こんくらいなら…2、3分で\n"
"解読できちゃうかな!\\!\n"
"お助けタイムの前にさー、\n"
"終わらせちゃっていい？"

#. ID 3, Page 7, Line 39, Pos (17,27)
msgid ""
"We tight.\\!\n"
"We tight."
msgstr ""
"ヨッシャーー。\\!\n"
"ジョージ、マジ頑張っちゃうから。"

#. ID 3, Page 7, Line 47, Pos (17,27)
msgid ""
"There's a pretty sweet\n"
"cafe southeast of here.\\!\n"
"Go grab some bites while\n"
"I work!"
msgstr ""
"南東の方にさ、チョー最高な\n"
"カフェがあんのよ。\\!\n"
"ウチが解読やってる間、\n"
"なんか食べてきちゃいな!"

#. ID 3, Page 7, Line 54, Pos (17,27)
msgid ""
"C'mon bud,\n"
"I can't wait forever."
msgstr ""
"ガンバレチビくん、\n"
"チョー楽しみにしてっから。"

#. ID 3, Page 7, Line 62, Pos (17,27)
msgid ""
"What are you waiting\n"
"for, bud?\\!\n"
"Go grab some grub!"
msgstr ""
"チビくん何待ち？\\!\n"
"さっさと腹ごしらえ、してきちゃいな!"

#. ID 3, Page 7, Line 70, Pos (17,27)
msgid ""
"Hey buddy!\\!\n"
"Uh, there was some,\\. like,\\.\n"
"totally weird stuff in that book.\\!\n"
"Here, read it yourself."
msgstr ""
"やっほーーチビくん!\\!\n"
"あー、\\.なんかさ、\\.すっげーヘンなこと\n"
"書いてあったんだわ。\\!\n"
"ほら、読んでみ。"

#. ID 3, Page 7, Line 78, Pos (17,27)
#. ID 13, Page 1, Line 170, Pos (11,25)
msgid "You are gonna save us, right?"
msgstr "ウチらのこと、救ってくれるよな？"

#. ID 4, Page 1, Line 2, Pos (19,22)
msgid "It's off."
msgstr "電源が切れてる。"

#. ID 13, Page 1, Line 3, Pos (11,25)
msgid ""
"There is an Entity few know about in this world.\\!\n"
"It has a habit of silencing those aware of it.\n"
"I'm one of the few still alive."
msgstr ""
"この世界にはほとんど知られていない\n"
"「存在」がある。\\!\n"
"それは、気付いた者を口封じをすることがある。\n"
"私はまだ生きている数少ない一人だ。"

#. ID 13, Page 1, Line 7, Pos (11,25)
msgid ""
"This being is somehow connected to the world.\n"
"Perhaps, it is the spirit of the world.\\!\n"
"Just as the light within our world fluctuates,\n"
"so does the temperament of this being."
msgstr ""
"この「存在」は、この世界と何らかの形で繋がって\n"
"いる。おそらく、それは世界の魂なのだろう。\\!\n"
"この世界の光が変動するのと同様に、\n"
"その「存在」の気質も変動する。"

#. ID 13, Page 1, Line 12, Pos (11,25)
msgid ""
"As the light is now fading, the Entity is now\n"
"seeking death.\\!\n"
"Death not to itself, but to our entire world."
msgstr ""
"光が消えつつある今、「存在」は死を求めている。\\!\n"
"自身の死ではなく、我々の世界全体の死だ。"

#. ID 13, Page 1, Line 16, Pos (11,25)
msgid "We must, of course, stop it."
msgstr "もちろん、我々は阻止せねばならない。"

#. ID 13, Page 1, Line 18, Pos (11,25)
msgid ""
"When our god and our savior arrive,\n"
"the Entity will attempt to manipulate them\n"
"into shattering the lightbulb at the top\n"
"of the spire."
msgstr ""
"我々の神と救世主が到着したら、\n"
"「存在」は彼らを操って塔の頂上にある電球を\n"
"砕かせようとするだろう。"

#. ID 13, Page 1, Line 23, Pos (11,25)
msgid ""
"Our god is the only thing this Entity can\n"
"communicate with; it is through them\n"
"that the savior will be tricked."
msgstr ""
"「存在」が唯一接触できるのは我らの神であり、\n"
"神を通して救世主は仕向けられるのだ。"

#. ID 13, Page 1, Line 27, Pos (11,25)
msgid ""
"Shattering the ligthbulb will \\c[3]return the savior\n"
"to their home world\\c[0], leaving ours to crumble.\\!\n"
"But, as far as we know, this is the \\c[3]only way for\n"
"the savior to return home\\c[0]."
msgstr ""
"電球を砕けば\\c[3]救世主は彼の世界に戻り\\c[0]、\n"
"我々の世界は崩壊する。\\!\n"
"しかし、我々の知る限り、これが\\c[3]救世主が帰還する\n"
"唯一の方法\\c[0]である。"

#. ID 13, Page 1, Line 32, Pos (11,25)
msgid ""
"What do we do in a situation like this?\\!\n"
"Tell the truth, causing the savior to leave?\\!\n"
"Lie, only to have the entity reveal the truth?"
msgstr ""
"このような状況で、我々はどうすれば\n"
"いいのだろうか？\\!\n"
"真実を告げ、救世主を帰らせるか？\\!\n"
"嘘を吐き、「存在」に真実を明かされるのか？"

#. ID 13, Page 1, Line 36, Pos (11,25)
msgid ""
"We can only hope they will have enough\n"
"respect for the world they've seen when\n"
"standing at the top of the spire and\n"
"juding our fates."
msgstr ""
"彼らが塔の頂上に立ち、我々の運命を裁くときに、\n"
"自分たちが見てきた世界に十分な敬意を\n"
"払ってくれることを願うしかない。"

#. ID 13, Page 1, Line 42, Pos (11,25)
msgid ".\\..\\.."
msgstr ""

#. ID 13, Page 1, Line 43, Pos (11,25)
msgid ""
"I don't want to end this world...\\!\n"
"Is that what will happen if I leave..?"
msgstr ""
"この世界が滅ぶのは嫌だよ…\\!\n"
"ミーが帰ったら、滅んじゃうの…？"

#. ID 13, Page 1, Line 48, Pos (11,25)
msgid ""
"I'm sure you realize the\n"
"importance of saving\n"
"ME, yes?"
msgstr ""
"この私を救うことの重要性は\n"
"理解しているわよね？"

#. ID 13, Page 1, Line 51, Pos (11,25)
msgid ""
"\"To enter the Tower is to\n"
"leave at the start.\"\n"
"That's what the book said."
msgstr ""
"「塔に立ち入ることは、\n"
"始まりから去ることである。」\n"
"本にそう書いてあったわ。"

#. ID 13, Page 1, Line 54, Pos (11,25)
msgid ""
"Now take this, and remember\n"
"my beauty forever."
msgstr ""
"ほら、これを持っていくのよ。\n"
"いつでも私の美しき顔を思い出せるわ。"

#. ID 13, Page 1, Line 59, Pos (11,25)
#. ID 13, Page 1, Line 82, Pos (11,25)
#. ID 13, Page 1, Line 102, Pos (11,25)
#. ID 13, Page 1, Line 121, Pos (11,25)
#. ID 13, Page 1, Line 143, Pos (11,25)
#. ID 13, Page 1, Line 164, Pos (11,25)
msgid "A die..."
msgstr "サイコロだ…"

#. ID 13, Page 1, Line 61, Pos (11,25)
msgid ""
"Hopefully it reminds you of\n"
"the terrible loss should you\n"
"decide to abandon us, yes?"
msgstr ""
"私たちを見捨てる決断を下したときに、\n"
"恐ろしい損失が待っているということも\n"
"思い起こさせてくれればいいんだけどね？"

#. ID 13, Page 1, Line 70, Pos (11,25)
msgid ""
"My honesty with you better\n"
"pay off, kid.\\!\n"
"Don't kill us."
msgstr ""
"アンタ、アタシの正直さに感謝しなさいよ。\\!\n"
"アタシたちを殺すなんてもってのほか。"

#. ID 13, Page 1, Line 73, Pos (11,25)
msgid ""
"\"To enter the Tower is to\n"
"leave at the start.\"\n"
"That's what the book said.\\!\n"
"Dunno what it means."
msgstr ""
"「塔に立ち入ることは、\n"
"始まりから去ることである。」\n"
"本にそう書いてあったわ。\\!\n"
"意味不明。"

#. ID 13, Page 1, Line 77, Pos (11,25)
msgid ""
"One last thing.\\!\n"
"Take this."
msgstr ""
"最後にもう一つ。\\!\n"
"これを持っていきなさい。"

#. ID 13, Page 1, Line 84, Pos (11,25)
msgid ""
"Keep that as a reminder\n"
"that there are people\n"
"who depend on you.\\!\n"
"Even me."
msgstr ""
"みーんな、アンタを頼りにしてるって\n"
"忘れないでよね。\\!\n"
"…アタシも。"

#. ID 13, Page 1, Line 88, Pos (11,25)
msgid "So don't screw up, please."
msgstr ""
"そんなワケで、お願いだから\n"
"しくじるんじゃないわよ。"

#. ID 13, Page 1, Line 93, Pos (11,25)
msgid ""
"Crazy.\\!\n"
"It's all crazy."
msgstr ""
"正気の沙汰じゃないわ…\\!\n"
"全部。"

#. ID 13, Page 1, Line 95, Pos (11,25)
msgid ""
"\"To enter the Tower is to\n"
"leave at the start.\"\n"
"Found that in a book."
msgstr ""
"「塔に立ち入ることは、\n"
"始まりから去ることである。」\n"
"そう本に書いてあった。"

#. ID 13, Page 1, Line 98, Pos (11,25)
msgid "Last thing."
msgstr "…最後に。"

#. ID 13, Page 1, Line 104, Pos (11,25)
msgid ""
"It's a gift.\\!\n"
"Go."
msgstr ""
"プレゼントよ。\\!\n"
"じゃあ、行ってきて。"

#. ID 13, Page 1, Line 112, Pos (11,25)
msgid "I know, that's soooo unfair..."
msgstr "分かってるよ、それってとーっても不公平…"

#. ID 13, Page 1, Line 113, Pos (11,25)
msgid ""
"\"To enter the Tower is to\n"
"leave at the start.\"\n"
"I found that in a book.\\!\n"
"I hope it helps!"
msgstr ""
"「塔に立ち入ることは、\n"
"始まりから去ることである。」\n"
"本に書いてあったんだ。\\!\n"
"助けになるといいな!"

#. ID 13, Page 1, Line 117, Pos (11,25)
msgid "Wait, one more thing!"
msgstr "待って、それからもうひとつ!"

#. ID 13, Page 1, Line 123, Pos (11,25)
msgid ""
"It's the cutest gift I had.\\!\n"
"I hope it reminds you of me\n"
"forever, 'kay?"
msgstr ""
"わたしが持ってる1番可愛いプレゼント。\\!\n"
"わたしのこと、ずっと忘れないでほしいな？"

#. ID 13, Page 1, Line 131, Pos (11,25)
msgid ""
"I'm sure it's overwhelming.\\!\n"
"But I'm sure you know in your\n"
"heart what the right choice is."
msgstr ""
"きっと圧倒されたと思うわ。\\!\n"
"でも、心の中では何が正しい選択か\n"
"分かっているはずよ。"

#. ID 13, Page 1, Line 134, Pos (11,25)
msgid ""
"\"To enter the Tower is to\n"
"leave at the start.\"\n"
"I found this after I finished\n"
"translating. It's all I could find."
msgstr ""
"「塔に立ち入ることは、\n"
"始まりから去ることである。」\n"
"解読した後に見つけたの。\n"
"見つけられたのはそれだけよ。"

#. ID 13, Page 1, Line 138, Pos (11,25)
msgid ""
"And, sweetie, before you\n"
"go, take this."
msgstr ""
"あと、かわいこちゃん、行く前に\n"
"これを持っていってちょうだい。"

#. ID 13, Page 1, Line 145, Pos (11,25)
msgid ""
"You're just so adorable I had\n"
"to give you something."
msgstr ""
"貴方はとっても可愛らしいから、\n"
"何かあげなきゃと思ってね。"

#. ID 13, Page 1, Line 153, Pos (11,25)
msgid ""
"So, like, not cool!\\!\n"
"Lame!"
msgstr ""
"ね、全っ然クールじゃない!\\!\n"
"ダサすぎ!"

#. ID 13, Page 1, Line 155, Pos (11,25)
msgid ""
"\"To enter the Tower is to\n"
"leave at the start.\"\n"
"I found that really weird thing\n"
"in one of my books."
msgstr ""
"「塔に立ち入ることは、\n"
"始まりから去ることである。」\n"
"ウチの本探したらさ、こんな文も\n"
"見つけたんだわ。"

#. ID 13, Page 1, Line 159, Pos (11,25)
msgid ""
"Oh hey pal, you should take\n"
"this too."
msgstr "そうだチビくん、これも持っていきな。"

#. ID 13, Page 1, Line 166, Pos (11,25)
msgid ""
"You're the coolest cat\n"
"hugng out with in a while!\\!\n"
"Maybe after you save the\n"
"world we could be bros!"
msgstr ""
"こんなにサイコーな猫チャンは\n"
"久しぶりだわ!\\!\n"
"アンタが世界救ったら後、\n"
"ウチら兄弟になれるっしょ!"

#. ID 14, Page 1, Line 2, Pos (20,26)
msgid ""
"My prophecy will be fulfilled.\n"
"The messiah will come."
msgstr ""
"私の預言は成就する。\n"
"救世主はやって来る。"

#. ID 14, Page 1, Line 5, Pos (20,26)
msgid ""
"I may not live long enough to\n"
"greet the messiah myself.\n"
"But the robot will take care\n"
"of that for me."
msgstr ""
"私は救世主を迎えるまで長生きできない\n"
"かもしれない。\n"
"しかし、ロボットが私の代わりに\n"
"願いを叶えてくれるだろう。"

#. ID 14, Page 1, Line 10, Pos (20,26)
msgid ""
"Here's to hoping it doesn't\n"
"malfunction before the time\n"
"comes."
msgstr ""
"その時が来る前に、ロボットが\n"
"故障しないことを祈りたい。"

#. ID 15, Page 1, Line 2, Pos (24,25)
msgid "Phosphor"
msgstr "螢光体"

#. ID 15, Page 1, Line 4, Pos (24,25)
msgid ""
"Blue phosphor comes in\n"
"both mineral and organic forms.\n"
"It is found on the surface of the \n"
"Barrens and inside seed shrimp."
msgstr ""
"靑色螢光体は鑛物形態および有機形態の\n"
"両方で存在する。\n"
"不毛の地の地表やエビの中から見つかる。"

#. ID 15, Page 1, Line 9, Pos (24,25)
msgid ""
"Green phosphor is primarily organic.\n"
"It is most commonly found inside \n"
"of moss and certain insects of the\n"
"glen."
msgstr ""
"綠色螢光体は有機形態が主である。\n"
"通常、コケや峡谷のある昆虫の中から見つかる。"

#. ID 15, Page 1, Line 14, Pos (24,25)
msgid ""
"Red phosphor is primarily liquid and \n"
"flows in the streets of the Refuge.\n"
"There is no known organic source\n"
"of red phosphor."
msgstr ""
"赤色螢光体は液体が主であり、\n"
"避難所の通りに流れている。\n"
"赤色螢光体の有機的な供給源は知られていない。"

#. ID 18, Page 1, Line 2, Pos (24,29)
msgid "The cycle shall begin anew."
msgstr "循環は新たに始まる。"

#. ID 20, Page 1, Line 2, Pos (29,29)
msgid "There are six."
msgstr "6つの面がある"

#. ID 20, Page 1, Line 4, Pos (29,29)
msgid "Which face did you get?"
msgstr "君はどの顔と遭遇した？"
